{"tid":2090561,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《卡巴拉島M》正式公開，高度還原PC版畫面，無縫地圖，實體碰撞","createTime":"2020-07-02T08:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T11:21:37.000Z","uid":109923,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4a5447dac7dbb6e8296510c0c7c7ab898c1ef3","tid":2090561,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ysUAV4Zfbes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FysUAV4Zfbes&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=7f4d056a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ysUAV4Zfbes</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8Mya3vHcscA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8Mya3vHcscA&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=4041b141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8Mya3vHcscA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bSclhzq7cBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbSclhzq7cBw&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=786a7a3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bSclhzq7cBw</a><br />\n<br />\nNTREEV多年前俾NCSOFT收購咗<br />\n養老hea咗咁多年終於有少少作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次《卡巴拉島M》有天堂M &amp; 天堂2M嘅元素加入<br />\n所以設計成無縫地圖，有實體碰撞，冇得穿人穿怪，走位企位好重要<br />\n至於天堂M &amp; 天堂2M嘅課金元素就....<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XbnRCZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXbnRCZL.jpg&h=2231757c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3qot6r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3qot6r.jpg&h=7c9a35fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2FjMS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2FjMS6.jpg&h=1e0ceb20&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAOhyx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAOhyx4.jpg&h=aa856321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑪奇mobile同天翼m都一直跳票，NCSOFT之前天堂M &amp; 天堂2M都一直好快手，今次分分鐘快手過NEXON出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f688f4f9995ee9b7959ec42dcbc51e8965e5743b","tid":2090561,"uid":61395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bda9658f714e3d3369008c9f82e12db106ffdd","tid":2090561,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:41:26.000Z","msg":"熱門舊OLG就嚟出齊手機版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便屌下NEXON老母，吊足咁多年胃口一隻都未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngungho幾時生性出返ECO手機版？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zo0hui82anA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZo0hui82anA&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=22b032c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Zo0hui82anA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vv99T4x3l88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVv99T4x3l88&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=71432890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vv99T4x3l88</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/V85X6D8gCY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FV85X6D8gCY8&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=cead6b7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/V85X6D8gCY8</a>"},{"pid":"2788d346ea35cd4930d87594049a7db7cae69ca8","tid":2090561,"uid":13767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"正阿喂..."},{"pid":"092f150e56417f0f880269a38aa82b4c5a2cc0c2","tid":2090561,"uid":109923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"卡巴拉島M 2020